as (Australian footballer)]] (1909\u20131966), Australian rules footballer\n** [[Reg Thomas (ice hockey)]] (born 1953), Canadian ice hockey player\n*** [[Reggie Thomas]], American politician from the state of Kentucky\n* [[Regena Thomas]], American politician\n* [[Regina D. Thomas]], American politician in Georgia\n* [[Reji Thomas]], American artist\n* [[Rekha R. Thomas]], American mathematician\n* [[Ren\u00e9 Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Ren\u00e9 Thomas (auto racing)]] (1886\u20131975), French motor racing champion and pioneer aviator\n** [[Ren\u00e9 Thomas (guitarist)]] (1927\u20131975), Belgian jazz guitarist\n** [[Ren\u00e9 Thomas (biologist)]] (born 1928), Belgian scientist\n* [[Reno Thomas]] (1922\u20132009), American politician in Pennsylvania\n* [[Rhodri Glyn Thomas]] (born 1953), Welsh politician\n* [[Rhys Thomas (comedian)]], multiple people\n** [[Rhys ap Thomas]] (1449\u20131525), Welsh soldier and landholder\n** [[Rhys Thomas (comedian)]] (born 1978), English comedian and actor\n** [[Rhys Thomas (juggler)]], American juggler, comedian and entertainer\n* [[Richard Thomas (disambiguation)|Richard, Richie, Ricki, Ricky and Ritchie Thomas (disambiguation)]], several people\n** [[Richard Thomas (Pennsylvania)]] (1744\u20131832), US Congressman from Pennsylvania\n** [[Richard Thomas (priest)]] (1753\u20131780), Welsh Anglican priest and antiquarian\n** [[Richard Thomas (civil engineer)]] (1779\u20131858), English civil engineer\n** [[Richard Thomas (Zarvona)]] (1833\u20131875), Confederate colonel and privateer known as \"the French lady\"\n*** [[Richie Thomas]] (born 1942), Welsh cricketer\n**** [[Ricki Thomas]], British writer\n***** [[Ricky Thomas]] (born 1965), American football player\n****** [[Ritchie Thomas]] (1915\u20131988), Australian rules footballer\n* [[Rob Thomas (disambiguation)]], several people\n** [[Rob Thomas (writer)]] (born 1965), television producer\n** [[Rob Thomas (musician)]] (born 1972), singer-songwriter, lead si