aller\n* [[Marcus Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Marcus Thomas (running back)]] (born 1984), American footballer\n** [[Marcus Thomas (actor)]], Belgian-born American film actor\n*[[Margaret Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Margaret Thomas]] (1842\u20131929), British-born Australian travel writer, poet and artist\n**[[Margaret Thomas (hymnwriter)]] (born 1779), Welsh hymnwriter\n**[[Margaret Thomas (painter)]] (1916-2016), British artist\n**[[Margaret Thomas (sport shooter)]] (born 1953), British sport shooter\n* [[Marjorie Thomas]] (1923\u20132008), English opera and oratorio singer\n* [[Mark Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Mark Thomas (MP)]], English politician who sat in the House of Commons in 1659\n** [[Mark Thomas]] (born 1963), English comedian, presenter, political satirist and reporter\n** [[Mark G. Thomas]] (born 1964), British evolutionary geneticist\n* [[Marlo Thomas]] (born 1937), American actress, daughter of Danny Thomas\n* [[Martin Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Martin Thomas, Baron Thomas of Gresford]] (born 1937), British Liberal Democrat politician\n** [[Martin Thomas (cricketer)]] (born 1952), English cricketer\n** [[Martin Thomas (footballer, born 1959)]], Welsh football player and goalkeeping coach\n** [[Martin Thomas (historian)]] (born 1964), British historian\n* [[Martyn Thomas]] (born 1948), British software engineer\n* [[Martyn Thomas (rugby player)]] (born 1987), Welsh rugby union player\n* [[Marvell Thomas]], American keyboard player\n* [[Mary Thomas (poet)|Mary Thomas]] (1787\u20131875), Australian poet and settler\n* [[Mary-Anne Thomas]] (born 1963), Australian politician in Victoria\n* [[Matthew Thomas (disambiguation)|Mathew, Matt and Matthew Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Mathew T. Thomas]] (born 1961), Indian politician\n*** [[Matt Thomas (ice hockey)]] (born 1975), Canadian ice hockey coach\n*** [[Matt Thomas (rugby league)]] (born 1976), Welsh r