 1983), Antiguan international footballer\n* [[Tammy Thomas]] (born 1970/71), disgraced American sprint cyclist\n* [[Tanisha Thomas]] (born 1985), American reality TV participant\n* [[Tarlos Thomas]] (born 1977), American footballer\n* [[Taryn Thomas]] (born 1983), American pornographic actress\n* [[Tavierre Thomas]] (born 1996), American football player\n* [[Ted Thomas (disambiguation)|Ted and Teddy Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n**[[Ted Thomas (judge)]] (born 1934), New Zealand jurist\n**[[Ted Thomas Sr.]] (born 1935), American cleric\n**[[Ted Thomas (footballer, born 1898)]] (1898\u20131965), Australian rules football player at the Melbourne Football Club\n**[[Ted Thomas (footballer, born 1922)]] (1922\u20131996), Australian rules football player at the North Melbourne Football Club\n**[[Ted Thomas (priest)]] (born 1927), British Church of England priest\n*** [[Teddy Thomas (rugby union)]] (born 1993), French rugby union player\n* [[Tennessee Thomas]] (born 1984), British drummer and actress\n* [[Terence Thomas, Baron Thomas of Macclesfield]] (1937\u20132018), British politician\n* [[Terrance Thomas]] (born 1980), American basketball player\n* [[Terrell Thomas]] (born 1985), American footballer\n* [[Terry Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Terry-Thomas]] (1911\u20131990), British comic actor\n** [[Terry Thomas (basketball)]] (born 1953), American basketball player\n** [[Terry Thomas (musician)]], English singer-songwriter and guitarist\n* [[Tessy Thomas]] (born 1964), Indian scientist\n* [[Theodore Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Theodore Gaillard Thomas]] (1832\u20131903), American gynecologist\n** [[Theodore Thomas (conductor)]] (1835\u20131905), American violinist and conductor\n** [[Theodore L. Thomas]] (born 1920), American science fiction writer\n* [[Thom Thomas]] (born 1941), American Playwright\n* [[Thomas Thomas (disambiguation)]], multiple people\n** [[Thomas Thomas (cleric)]] (1804\u20131877), Welsh cleric (\